code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     EtcdStatsEndpoint endpoint = getEndpoint().     Object answer = endpoint.getStats(getClient()).     if (answer != null) {         exchange.getIn().setHeader(EtcdConstants.ETCD_NAMESPACE, getNamespace()).         exchange.getIn().setHeader(EtcdConstants.ETCD_PATH, getPath()).         exchange.getIn().setBody(answer).     } }
